description: Once upon a time, in a world filled with animals of all shapes and sizes, there existed a secret society of weasels who believed that their kind was superior to all others. The Ordinal Weasels had a singular purpose: to rule the world. They believed that they had been chosen by a higher power to achieve this goal and had been working towards it for centuries, manipulating events and pulling strings behind the scenes..
name: Ordinal Weasels
